# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# The repo root's .gitignore has a `*.test` rule (Go's compiled-test-binary
# convention) that would otherwise also swallow Vite's `.env.test` — vitest
# runs in Vite's "test" mode and auto-loads exactly that filename (see
# .env.test's own comment), so it needs to stay tracked.
!.env.test

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
